<div class="text">
<span class="date">July 3, 2020</span>
<h2><a href="https://www.texasstandard.org/stories/my-socially-distanced-path-to-citizenship/">My Socially Distanced Path To&nbsp;Citizenship</a></h2>
<p>As an immigrant, you know the United States doesnt wait for you. Instead, you wait for the United Statesto closely scrutinize your life, to see value in you.</p>
